com.darkfoxdev.tesi.targetlint.targets

Class Target

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.darkfoxdev.tesi.targetlint.targets.Target

  • public class Target
extends java.lang.Object
    The type Target. This type defines the search target on which the detector will work. A target is defined by a search level, an element type (see tlast package) and a list of filters. Those allows to get only relevant elements as matches.
